*mhonarc-2.6.16 (19 Oct 2006)

  19 Oct 2006; Ilya A. Volynets-Evenbakh <iluxa@gentoo.org>
  +mhonarc-2.6.16.ebuild:
  Version bump

  07 Oct 2006; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> mhonarc-2.6.15.ebuild:
  Making 2.6.15 stable on x86, mips, and sparc. Alpha, amd64, and ppc can
  follow suit when they want, then 2.6.10/11 will get axed. Also adding a fix
  for Bug #123134.

